      "name": "Rejuvenation",
      "sort": 500000,
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Setting right the injustice that led to the commoner's death allows it to move on to the afterlife.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>When a ghost is destroyed, it re-forms after [[/br 2d4 #days]]{2d4 days} within the location it's bound to, fully healed. A ghost can be permanently destroyed only if someone determines the reason for its existence and sets right whatever prevents the spirit from resting.</p>"
        },
        "source": {
